title: Entering an Amusement Park part - b

content.question: The price of admission to the park is $15 until 5:00 P.M. (t = 17). After 5:00 P.M., the price of admission to the park is $11. How many dollars are collected from admissions to the park on the given day? Round your answer to the nearest whole number.
